<h1>About Our Book Library</h1>

<h2>Data Sources</h2>
<p>This application collects and displays information about books, authors, genres, and libraries. The data is sourced from four different places:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Faker Gem:</strong> Used to generate fake authors, genres, and additional libraries. This provides a base set of data for testing and demonstration.</li>
  <li><strong>Books CSV Data:</strong> A CSV file containing information about classic books, including titles, descriptions, publication years, and author names.</li>
  <li><strong>Libraries CSV Data:</strong> A CSV file with real library locations including addresses, coordinates, phone numbers, and websites.</li>
  <li><strong>Additional Faker Books:</strong> More books generated using Faker to reach the minimum record count, assigned to existing authors.</li>
</ul>

