<h2>Database Schema</h2>
<p>The database consists of five main tables:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Authors:</strong> Stores author information (name, bio).</li>
  <li><strong>Genres:</strong> Stores genre information (name, description).</li>
  <li><strong>Books:</strong> Stores book information (title, description, published_year, author_id).</li>
  <li><strong>BookGenres:</strong> Join table for many-to-many relationship between books and genres.</li>
  <li><strong>Libraries:</strong> Stores library information (name, address, latitude, longitude, phone, website).</li>
</ul>

<p>Relationships:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Author has_many Books</li>
  <li>Book belongs_to Author</li>
  <li>Book has_many Genres through BookGenres</li>
  <li>Genre has_many Books through BookGenres</li>
</ul>

